<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Apollonopolis Magna</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><g type="stauros"/> ἀπέκαμον γράφων παρενοχλῶν τοῖς θεοφυλάκτοις καὶ <expan>μεγαλ<ex cert="high">ο</ex>π<ex cert="high">ρεπεστάτοις</ex></expan> ὑμῖν περὶ τῶν γοναχίων, καὶ οὐδὲν ἤνυσα εἰ μὴ τὰ χαρτία 

    <lb n="2"/>ἅπερ δαπανῶ. καὶ αἰσχύνομαι καθάπα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ξ</supplied> γράφων ὑμῖν περὶ τούτου, διότι, ὡς βλέπω, τὸ πρᾶγμα οὐκ ἀρέσκει ὑμῖν. 

    <lb n="3"/>καὶ πρὸ τοῦ ἐμὲ γὰρ κατελθεῖν ἐκ τῶν ἄν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ω</supplied>, ἐδεξάμην μίαν <num value="1"/> ἐπιστολὴν ὑμῶν περιέχουσαν ὡς εἰς τὰ ἱστάριά <choice><corr>ἐστιν</corr><sic>εισιν</sic></choice>. παρακαλῶ οὖν 

    <lb n="4"/>ὑμᾶς, εἴπερ ἰσχύει ἡ παράκλησίς μου, πεμφθῆναί μοι αὐτὰ διὰ Σεργίου 

τοῦ στρατιώτου. ἀσπάζομαι δὲ ὑμᾶς διὰ τοῦ <expan>γράμμ<ex cert="high">ατος</ex></expan> <g type="stauros"/> 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="5"/>τῷ <expan>θεοφυλ<ex cert="high">άκτῳ</ex></expan> μου <expan>δεσπό<ex cert="high">τῃ</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">καὶ</ex></expan> <expan>πατρ<ex cert="high">ὶ</ex></expan> Παπᾷ τῷ <expan>μεγ<ex cert="high">ίστῳ</ex></expan> <expan>παγ<ex cert="high">άρ</ex>χ<ex cert="high">ῳ</ex></expan> <expan>Ἀπόλ<ex cert="high">λωνος Ἄνω</ex></expan> <g type="stauros"/> Κολλοῦθος <expan>ν<ex cert="high">ο</ex>τ<ex cert="high">άριος</ex></expan> <g type="stauros"/> </ab></div></div><div n="meta.20255" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.20255" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" precision="low" notBefore="0675" notAfter="0676">ca. 675 - 676 (?)</date></p><p><date type="textDate" precision="low" notBefore="0660" notAfter="0661">ca. 660 - 661 (?)</date></p></div><div n="meta.20255" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Alternativdatierung: ca. 660 - 661. Zur Datierung vgl. ZPE 49, 1982, S. 88.</p></div><div n="meta.20255" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.20255" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Apoll.</title><biblScope type="numbers">50</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">20255</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0061</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">50</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0061;;50" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.20255" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><hea